title: ‘The Circle’ Season 4 Finale! Plus, an Interview With the Season 4 Winner. | Netflix and Spill
description:
Jomi and Jodi take us through the finale of ‘The Circle’ Season 4 (0:35), then Jomi speaks with Season 4 winner Frank about his strategy going into ‘The Circle,’ what it felt like winning with friends all around him, and much more (46:25).
Hosts: Jomi Adeniran and Jodi Walker
Guest: Frank Grimsley
Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Chelsea Stark-Jones
